description: This New York City guide skill provides helpful travel information to NYC visitors and residents alike.  You can ask for top attractions as well as suggestions for things to do in New York City.  You can also ask for local NYC news to assist in planning a fun trip.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask New York Guide for attractions.
Alexa, ask New York Guide for the top five things to do.
name: NYC Guide
shortDescription: Get attractions, top five things to do, and local news for New York City.
